{"tid":1895100,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"韓國女主播疑染武漢肺炎 直播途中緊急送院","createTime":"2020-02-24T10:46:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-01T05:54:16.000Z","uid":132587,"like":168,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"b1bd67985c4eadc6f681c64f22929de7bc91e1c3","tid":1895100,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T10:46:55.000Z","msg":"韓女主播疑染武漢肺炎 轉播一半不適急就醫<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎（COVID-19、新冠肺炎）疫情在全球不斷擴大，目前死亡人數已超過2003年爆發的SARS（嚴重急性呼吸道症候群）。除了爆發地中國外，南韓成為第二嚴重的國家，截至24日9時，確診病例已達763人，死亡人數為7名，我國外交部也宣佈調升南韓旅遊警示至黃色，因第31例確診感染的這位61歲「毒后」感染後還到處趴趴走，造成全韓通通淪陷，高達8725人還在檢查中。而今天一位晨間新聞女主播兼氣象播報員也出現了疑似發病的症狀，檢查中結果將於下午出爐。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/02/24/2422650-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F02%2F24%2F2422650-XXL.jpg&h=e1c716d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲金敏兒出現發熱的症狀，正在接受檢查中。（圖／翻攝自YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n據韓媒報導，今（24日）早，JTBC電視台相關人士表示，女主播金敏兒（김민아）因發熱的症狀，正在接受了武漢肺炎的檢查，所以早上原本預計播出的晨間新聞時段先停播，考量到因為電視台視密閉空間，接觸到的人又不少，為了以防萬一，目前除了金敏兒本人，製作組其他工作人員也都先進行自我隔離，檢查的結果將於今天下午出爐。<br />\n<br />\n▼金敏兒目前和製作組其他工作人員都在進行自我隔離。（圖／翻攝自金敏兒IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/szS34wk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FszS34wk.jpg&h=c12dadb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而也是英雄聯盟南韓賽區賽事（LCK）主持人的金敏兒，昨（23日）天出席在首爾鐘路區LoL PARK LCK Arena舉辦的「2020英雄聯盟韓國冠軍聯賽」，賽事上，她就已出現了37.5度低燒的症狀，所以提前離場，立刻到醫院就診，她也在IG上表示「我的症狀並不是太嚴重，所以確診的可能性應該很小」，和對因為我而感到不安的人致上歉意，稱一定會把檢查結果公佈給大家。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=695236\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D695236&d=MxNsT%2FmsUjaXWzHBtsAqwRnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=0e43ff23\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D695236&h=bae3e9e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=695236</a>"},{"pid":"50868a337fb6c63b145592403c2206a294ba21ad","tid":1895100,"uid":132587,"like":73,"dislike":8,"score":65,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T10:48:26.000Z","msg":"事發突然，金敏兒怕粉絲擔心，就在個人IG上透露自身狀況，比如體溫超過37.5度、身體痠痛等，「雖然沒有值得擔心的症狀、罹病的機率也很低，但出於不能隨意判斷的想法，因此離開了現場」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://news.cts.com.tw/photo/cts/202002/20200224-624678.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cts.com.tw%2Fphoto%2Fcts%2F202002%2F20200224-624678.png&h=3bb39f75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n金敏兒在個人IG上透露自身狀況。(翻攝金敏兒IG)<br />\n<br />\n南韓確診例不斷增加 女主播檢疫報告晚間出爐<br />\n由於目前正處於武漢肺炎疫情高峰，因此金敏兒所屬JTBC電視台今早也發佈聲明，宣佈暫時停播她的晨間新聞節目，並出於安全考量，要求其組內相關工作人在家自主隔離。<br />\n<br />\n金敏兒的武漢肺炎檢疫報告將在今日晚間出爐，她也在IG承諾一定會在第一時間將檢驗結果告訴大家。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://news.cts.com.tw/photo/cts/202002/20200224-624680.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cts.com.tw%2Fphoto%2Fcts%2F202002%2F20200224-624680.png&h=37ef4b11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://news.cts.com.tw/photo/cts/202002/20200224-624681.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cts.com.tw%2Fphoto%2Fcts%2F202002%2F20200224-624681.jpg&h=86d84391&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n金敏兒擁有姣好外型，擁有不少粉絲。(翻攝金敏兒IG)"},{"pid":"30beea22daa2771a6f8270e0cd29c4312f36c8fe","tid":1895100,"uid":38904,"like":83,"dislike":2,"score":81,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T10:51:31.000Z","msg":"病毒經大氣電波傳染<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"170c99d465629b22d7de522b0696441aaf478763","tid":1895100,"uid":309935,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T10:51:54.000Z","msg":"仆街支那"},{"pid":"5aafdd6e9268289576ccac0886cfe6a26ab2238b","tid":1895100,"uid":86204,"like":81,"dislike":6,"score":75,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T10:52:01.000Z","msg":"韓國d主搵播個個都好正"},{"pid":"126fc499c7d724c4ece6b2ac9fcb65eeb0d68b6b","tid":1895100,"uid":78470,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T10:52:33.000Z","msg":"lck<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"286b4b84cf988276482b854545b9e2a3c1863f17","tid":1895100,"uid":197640,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T10:55:26.000Z","msg":"好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d360e1e09cb15c627a458beda51f9e25b981f415","tid":1895100,"uid":11013,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T10:55:58.000Z","msg":"幫推 <br />\n<br />\n唔好意思 借一借位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非 手足 家長 學生都請入黎 <br />\n<br />\ntg 支足channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/materials201920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmaterials201920&d=MxNsT%2FmsUjaXWzHBtsAqwRnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=8e36a079\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/materials201920</a>"},{"pid":"8d71137f8f7fa691ed39f579b7369f05641d00a0","tid":1895100,"uid":172349,"like":115,"dislike":5,"score":110,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T11:01:31.000Z","msg":"應該有好多男高層受感染"},{"pid":"8c17a8470c536972e5d7d1c090d9d37acf6cee7d","tid":1895100,"uid":181655,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T11:04:15.000Z","msg":"高層大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a60f675a5da6537ff3dfcb24f76c979ccef2a841","tid":1895100,"uid":40272,"like":50,"dislike":8,"score":42,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T11:08:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uGOOvZq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuGOOvZq.jpg&h=801a9492&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c5092d6b7c8c5a6b197824543474cbf277731da","tid":1895100,"uid":49144,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"30beea22daa2771a6f8270e0cd29c4312f36c8fe","tid":1895100,"uid":38904,"like":83,"dislike":2,"score":81,"cited