kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cts.com.tw%2Fphoto%2Fcts%2F202002%2F20200224-624680.png&h=37ef4b11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://news.cts.com.tw/photo/cts/202002/20200224-624681.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cts.com.tw%2Fphoto%2Fcts%2F202002%2F20200224-624681.jpg&h=86d84391&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n金敏兒擁有姣好外型，擁有不少粉絲。(翻攝金敏兒IG)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T12:28:38.000Z","msg":"大家一齊推動韓國民意做野啊<br />\n<br />\n（國際戰線）借助日韓爆發武肺推動全球反奶共運動和全球排支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1894747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1894747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"27a1fd4f0ff05d25ecb5fb02ddfe7e064f87ebbf","tid":1895100,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"726fabf1dc902063934c2511561df15746cba4a5","tid":1895100,"uid":214784,"like":15,"dislike":4,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T11:23:40.000Z","msg":"病毒可寄宿於精液中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n男高層rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T12:57:07.000Z","msg":"你應該話愛液中"}]}